{"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B34ThemeButtonComponentTokensProviderC","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of buttons"}]},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"button"}]},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSButton"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"